  "title": "Gardener | Plant Nursery / Landscape Worker | Sengkang / Tiong Bahru | 9755",
  "description": "<p><p><strong>Role: Gardener | Plant Nursery / Landscape Worker</strong><br /><strong>Industry: Landscaping & Plantation</strong><br /><strong>5.5 Days Per Week | Sunday OFF | 8am-5pm (Mon to Fri) | 8am to 12pm (Sat)</strong><br /><strong>Basic Salary: SGD $1,950 [ Fix ]</strong><br /><strong>Entitled to Medical Benefits & Bonus</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li><p><strong>Must be Covid vaccination certified due to the work environment at hospitals.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Prefer those with basic plantation knowledge and gardener experience.</strong></p></li></ol><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Weeding and mulching landscape beds</p></li><li><p>Trimming small trees, hedges and shrubs</p></li><li><p>Removing unwanted, dead or damaged trees</p></li><li><p>Planting shrubs, flowers and trees</p></li><li><p>Watering gardens, lawns and landscapes</p></li><li><p>Grass cutting</p></li><li><p>Fertilizing plants</p></li><li><p>Monitoring and maintaining plant health<br /><br />Tai Jia Seng Reg No: R26159755</p><p>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p></li></ul></p>",
